headline : Turkish mining disaster trial starts in Soma
text : \r\nAlmost one year on, the bereaved in the Soma mining disaster are preparing for the trial against the mine's management. 301 miners died in Turkey's worst mining accident when a tunnel caught fire. But should government officials also be in the dock? Some people in Soma think they should.\r\n
